<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .dcc-logo {
            height: 25px;
        }

        .verify-button {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .extra-message,
        .extra-url {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        button {
            background-color: green;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0px 2px 1.5px orangered;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .button-url {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <img src="templates/DCC_LOGO.png" alt="" class="dcc-logo">
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
	<p>Dear {{name}},</p>
	<p>We received a request to reset your password for username - {{username}}. The OTP to reset your password is {{otp}}.
	
	<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</p>
    <p class="extra-message">This OTP is valid only for <strong> 5 minutes</strong>.</p>
	<p>Thank you,</p>
	<p>DCC, NITA</p>
    <br></br>
    <p class="extra-message"><strong>Developers and Coders Club, NIT Agartala</strong></p>
</body>

</html>